Mapon GO 2021 is a new and improved version of the Mapon driver mobile application and is available to all registered Mapon platform users. It's still at an early stage of development and offers only a fraction of the features currently available on Mapon GO. However, we're expecting to expand the functionality of Mapon GO 2021 in the future. What's more, the new app already offers such added benefits as GPS tracking, as well as enhanced overall application speed and design for better user experience.     
The Mapon GO 2021 application is an effective tool capable of improving overall business efficiency. It gives the opportunity for drivers to communicate and exchange important information with the back-office in a digitised space. Less paper, faster communication, easy information access and more!

 FEATURES:
* Dashboard - for easy overview and access to relevant information;
* Messaging - for keeping in touch with the back office, forwarding tasks and making sure no files, orders or pictures go missing;
* Mobile tracking - provides built-in mobile tracker functionality; 
* Route history - a complete log with all of the driver's previous travels;
* Settings - for easy set-up and customisation;
* Login.

